		background: #007aff;
		box-shadow: 0 4rpx 12rpx rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.3);
	}
	
	.btn-secondary {
		background: #34c759;
		box-shadow: 0 4rpx 12rpx rgba(52, 199, 89, 0.3);
	}
	
	.btn-danger {
		background: #ff3b30;
